{{Infobox person | name = Carl Jan Granqvist | image = Carl Jan Granqvist 01.JPG | caption = Carl Jan Granqvist (2010) | birth_date ={{Birth date and age|1946|3|22|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Örebro]], [[Sweden]] | occupation = | known_for = | height = }}
'''''Carl Jan'' Erik Granqvist''', (born 22 March 1946) is a Swedish [[restaurateur]], food and wine connoisseur and television personality, as well as professor in the art of food at the ''Norsk hotellhøgskole'' in [[Stavanger]], which is part of the [[University of Stavanger]].<ref>[http://www.uis.no/om_uis/samfunnsvitskapleg_fakultet/norsk_hotellhoegskole_-_oekonomi_og_leiing/ Leiing - Carl Jan Granqvist] Retrieved 3 January 2015. {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070425203915/http://www.uis.no/om_uis/samfunnsvitskapleg_fakultet/norsk_hotellhoegskole_-_oekonomi_og_leiing/ |date=April 25, 2007 }}</ref> He studied art history at [[Stockholm University]] between 1967 and 1968. Between 1969 and 1970 he studied at Virginska restaurangskolan, a restaurant school, in [[Örebro]]. He has also done an internship at [[Operakällaren]] between 1970 and 1972.
Carl Jan Granqvist became the kellermeister of [[Grythyttans gästgivaregård]] in 1972 and was later responsible for creating Måltidens hus and the Restaurant school in [[Grythyttan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.romantiskweekend.se/romantiska-hotell-i-grythyttan/grythyttans-gastgiveregard|title=» Romantisk weekend – Grythyttans Gästgiveregård – Boka direkt!|publisher=romantiskweekend.se|accessdate=3 January 2015}}</ref> He was a pioneer in Sweden with the [[sapere method]] which means that the composition of a meal not only considers the smell but also the guests other senses. He was the founder of Vinkällaren Grappe at [[Östermalm]] in [[Stockholm]], the first commercial wine storage facility of its kind in Sweden, which started its business in 1986.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mitti.se/carl-jans-skattkammare/|title=Carl Jans skattkammare|work=mitti.se|accessdate=3 January 2015}}</ref>
He has participated in several TV shows since his debut in 1983 on [[Sveriges Television|SVT]] with the wine tasting show ''Levande livet''. He has also competed in the show [[På spåret]] along with [[Lotta Bromé]] on several occasions and they won the 1998 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vk.se/712130/klassiska-par-tavlar-i-pa-sparet?mobil |title=Klassiska par tävlar i "På spåret" |publisher=vk.se |accessdate=3 January 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103230311/http://www.vk.se/712130/klassiska-par-tavlar-i-pa-sparet?mobil |archivedate=January 3, 2015 }}</ref> He was also co-host for the show between 2004 and 2005 along with [[Ingvar Oldsberg]]. In 2006 he hosted the show ''Carl Jans änglar'' on [[TV3 (Sweden)|TV3]]. The same year he was a guest on the [[Kanal 5 (Sweden)|Kanal 5]] show [[Boston Tea Party (TV series)|Boston Tea Party]] hosted by [[Filip Hammar and Fredrik Wikingsson|Filip and Fredrik]].<ref>[http://kanal5.se/web/guest/bostonteaparty/avsnitt?p_p_lifecycle=0&p_p_id=K5AV_INSTANCE_4FvH&_K5AV_INSTANCE_4FvH_articleId=1189450 Boston Tea Party Filip och Fredrik] Retrieved 3 January 2015. {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120525085621/http://kanal5.se/web/guest/bostonteaparty/avsnitt?p_p_lifecycle=0&p_p_id=K5AV_INSTANCE_4FvH&_K5AV_INSTANCE_4FvH_articleId=1189450 |date=25 May 2012 }}</ref> In 2009 he was a celebrity dancer in [[Let's Dance (Swedish TV series)|Let's Dance]] broadcast on [[TV4 (Sweden)|TV4]].
Granqvist is a member of the [[Freemasonry in Sweden#Swedish Order of Freemasons|Swedish Freemasons Order]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ullgrenhistoria.se/bocker/hemligheternas%20brodraskap/hemligheternas%20brodraskap.html |title=Ullgren Historia |publisher=ullgrenhistoria.se |accessdate=3 January 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321134808/http://ullgrenhistoria.se/bocker/hemligheternas%20brodraskap/hemligheternas%20brodraskap.html |archivedate=March 21, 2014 }}</ref> In his autobiographic book ''Människan, mötena, måltiden'', Granqvist revealed that he is [[bisexual]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.expressen.se/index.jsp?a=82123|title=Carl Jan har sex med både män och kvinnor|work=Expressen|accessdate=3 January 2015}}</ref>
