'''Yara Naoum''' ({{lang-ar|يارا نعوم}}, born 1 September 1987 in [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]]) is an [[Egypt]]ian [[beauty queen]]. She is married to the Egyptian Football player [[Emad Moteab]].{{Citation needed|date=August 2011}} She earned the title of Miss Egypt in 2008.

